  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Benson Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "John 10:37-39",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "John 10:37-39",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "If I do not the works of my Father, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "&c. — When I claim the character of ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "the Son of God, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "I do not expect to be credited merely on my own affirmation: if I do not such glorious works as could not be performed by any but a divine agent, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "believe me not: but if I do ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— If it be apparent that I do such works, though you believe not me, and are regardless of my own testimony in the case, yet, at least, believe the works; and let their evidence remove the prejudices you have entertained; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "that ye may know,",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " &c",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "., that the Father is in me, and I in him — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Namely, by such a union as abundantly justifies the expression which seems to give you such peculiar offence. In other words, Though ye do not believe what I say concerning my personal dignity, on my own authority, you ought to believe it on account of my miracles, which are plainly of such a kind, that it is impossible for any deceiver to perform them; they are the works of God himself, and therefore you ought to consider them as such. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Therefore they sought again to take him ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— For this defence was so far from pacifying them, that they were rather the more enraged at him through it. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "But he escaped out of their hand ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— Withdrew himself, as he had done before, in an extraordinary manner. See ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "John 8:59",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Luke 4:30",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "",
        "children": []
      }
